    "#Machine Learning for Chronic Kidney Disease Outcome Prediction\n",
    "##Dataset\n",
    "We use the Community Screening split of the electricsheepafrica/chronic-kidney-disease dataset from HuggingFace — a synthetic dataset generated from real-world epidemiological distributions across African community screening programmes.\n",
    "1. Environment Setup"
